### 🧠 Check Server Health
GET http://localhost:8000/

### 🧍‍♀️ Register New User
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/registration/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password1": "StrongPassword123!",
  "password2": "StrongPassword123!"
}

###

### 🔐 Login User (email/password)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPassword123!"
}

###

### 🔑 Google Login with Access Token
# Replace ACCESS_TOKEN with your real Google access token
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/social/google/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "access_token": ""
}

###

### 🍏 Apple Login with Identity Token
# Replace ID_TOKEN with your real Apple identity token
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/social/apple/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "access_token": "APPLE_ID_TOKEN"
}

###

### 🔁 Get JWT Refresh
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/token/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### 🚪 Logout
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/logout/
Content-Type: application/json
